{"tid":274380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數據揭密 窮人才用Android手機？","createTime":"2017-06-07T09:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T10:41:38.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2173372228df9d698f27c41421143bd615a8363c","tid":274380,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"一年一度的WWDC(蘋果全球開發者大會)已於美西時間6月5日起跑，蘋果執行長Tim Cook照幾年來的習慣，再度在演講台上針對Android系統的升級率與碎片化揶揄了一番。不僅如此，日本調查機構《AUNCON》先前發表的《2017全球智慧型手機市占率調查》中，還發現了國民平均所得越高的國家，iOS市占越高的結果，又是另一個會讓不少Android手機廠商感到尷尬的事實。<br />\n<br />\n《AUNCON》今年2月份針對國民生產毛額(GDP)全球排名前40位的國家，進行了智慧型手機市占率的調查。在人均GDP與人均總總收入(GNI)都名列前茅的北歐四國：瑞士、丹麥、瑞典與挪威，iOS的市占率都高於Android。北美洲的部分，人均收入比較高的美國跟加拿大，同樣也是iOS占優勢，而人均收入較低的墨西哥，則是Android占優勢，高達80.9%。在亞洲地區唯一的例外則是南韓，Android市占高達81.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在亞洲國家當中，結果也很類似，在日本iOS市占高達68.9%。人均收入較高的新加坡，iOS市占(33.5%)雖然不比Android(52.1%)高，不過包含台灣(iOS市占30.9%)、香港(iOS市占41.2%)，都比人均所得較低的馬來西亞(iOS市占13.6%)還要高。位在大西洋的澳大利亞與紐西蘭，iOS市占也都偏高，分別是40.7%與45.6%。而在入選的40國內，非洲僅有三國，在埃及、奈及利亞以及南非的Android市占分別是89.9%、73.2%與71.7%。<br />\n<br />\n根據《AUNCON》統計，全球iOS市占最高的十國依序是：日本(68.9%)、瑞士(59.3%)、澳大利亞(57.4%)、美國(54.0%)、挪威(53.1%)、瑞典(52.8%)、加拿大(52.7%)、丹麥(49.4%)、英國(49.2%)、紐西蘭(45.6%)。據世界銀行2016年的統計，以上最愛用iPhone的十國，人均GPD超過35000美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前用ip"},{"pid":"b8c6d12364dae3c3efcf79a19da0fdeaeab94aa3","tid":274380,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"南韓智能電話用家，大部分會用巨擘企業牌子嘅 Android 電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c06b4624be1ec0362edc80bda4d292ee4c8dfc","tid":274380,"uid":45285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"真心覺得蘋果好可憐&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸左都要撐&hellip;"},{"pid":"9db1b7c0f21002d284e7918dfff2080666d6eb48","tid":274380,"uid":72825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心覺得蘋果好可憐&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸左都要撐&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n依家仲有人用iphone既咩？"},{"pid":"60bd81f8fcb2926b3002419b24341d3094885adb","tid":274380,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"真心唔希望apple輪落到要咁樣打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAndroid做到幾百蚊至幾萬蚊一部都得，百貨應百客，呢樣apple都唔會行架啦。比條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d74436d0fed225e7ff0a196dd5139fdd0b2b8f3","tid":274380,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e5qxghp7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe5qxghp7&h=fd4af3c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b901c12ff80d1b2ee9409dc96754e6e6b5cdb0cf","tid":274380,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a18962d81143f01ae00915cb7fe812c89dd3ce3","tid":274380,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心覺得蘋果好可憐&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸左都要撐&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n依家仲有人用iphone既咩？</blockquote><br />\n周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAn狗係窮人代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49b9e31ccf20965ee66d8857c48a375dd573ccd","tid":274380,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:48:10.000Z","msg":"岩呀 等班窮撚買iphone裝備自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729c5275865cbcb473eb8d78027b50fa07d4ecd0","tid":274380,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"屌好心你睇下個定價先，咁都有得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj